These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, hot-chocolate, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, parkour, tennis, lacrosse
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, turtle
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, reading, magic-tricks, dancing
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage          | tea     | mirinda   | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Sport   | parkour | swimming    | lacrosse   | tennis    |
| Pet           | goat       | turtle   | cat   | bird     |
| Hobby     | reading       | traveling | dancing  | magic-tricks      |

