.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, balloon-flower, begonia, orchid
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, cycling, snowboarding, surfing
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, engineer, videographer, coach
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
 2. the videographer is in an odd position##4
 3. the coach is the person who growsazalea##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the engineer##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 8. the coach is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the engineer is the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the coach is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Flower      | balloon-flower       | azalea | orchid     | begonia     |
| Sport   | cycling      | water-polo       | surfing | snowboarding |
| Job           | videographer       | coach    | engineer     | writer         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

