.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, lavender, pink, aquamarine
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, august, february, october
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, rock, techno
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, writer, accountant
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 6. the accountant is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the journalist##1
 8. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
 9. the journalist is in an even position##4
10. the accountant is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is the journalist##1
12. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | aquamarine    | pink      | lavender   | grey |
| Birthday   | december | february | august | october  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | rock         | blues  | techno  |
| Job           | writer      | journalist          | accountant | paramedic  |

