House: tower, gothic-revival, palace, farmhouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, western, satire, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, lacrosse, tennis
 1. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 4. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person eating pumpkin##5
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person eating watermelon##5
 6. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
 7. the person eating pumpkin is between the person watching western movies and the person eating asparagus##2
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
10. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
11. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
12. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the person eating pear##5
13. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Food      | pear | watermelon     | pumpkin        | asparagus      |
| House           | gothic-revival    | farmhouse   | palace | tower |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | western    | romance        | satire         |
| Sport         | baseball    | lacrosse | tennis         | handball    |

