The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite, poppy, sunflower
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, skateboard, taxi
 1. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
 4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5
 6. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person who growspoppy##1
10. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
11. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
12. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
