 1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person drinking coffee and the fan of funk##2
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 3. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the fan of funk is the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 7. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
10. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
11. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
