 3. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the scientist##3
 5. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
