 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
10. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
11. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the davidoff-smoker##5
12. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
13. the person watching epic movies is the havana-smoker##1

