.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, cycling, surfing, weightlifting
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, dancing, hiking, singing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, balloon-flower, rose, azalea
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Sport          | cycling    | weightlifting        | surfing     | sailing          |
| Hobby           | dancing | hiking        | fishing | singing |
| Flower   | azalea    | tulip     | rose      | balloon-flower        |

