.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, snowboarding, lacrosse
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, singing, chess, dancing
City: paris, colone, marseilles, san-francisco
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
10. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Sport           | lacrosse   | volleyball  | water-polo        | snowboarding |
| Hobby   | reading     | dancing     | chess      | singing   |
| City     | colone | marseilles | san-francisco          | paris     |

