.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, blend, prince, ritmeester
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
House: cottage, craftsman, colonial, townhouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, trike, helicopter, bike
 1. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 2. the person driving the bike is the havana-smoker##1
 3. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 7. the social-worker is the townhouse house##1
 8. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
10. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
11. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5
12. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar          | havana | prince  | ritmeester    | blend       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| House   | craftsman    | colonial   | townhouse  | cottage     |
| Transport   | bike      | helicopter    | trike        | ship |

 